he helped to form.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.760
He also graduated from the American
Baptist Theological Seminary.

00:03:00.760 --> 00:03:04.650
At 23, he was an architect
and keynote speaker

00:03:04.650 --> 00:03:15.050
